snippet.title: Go-Go Town! - Official Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description:
In this latest trailer for Go-Go Town!, get a peek at building and farming elements, and more from this upcoming life simulator game. A playtest for Go-Go Town will be available on July 3, 2023. In Go-Go Town, as mayor, it’s up to you to breathe life back into this rundown town. Construct shops, hire staff, automate deliveries with couriers, and attract tourists to town, all while managing infrastructure and avoiding catastrophes. Who said being mayor was going to be easy?

#SummerOfGaming
